    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior paint retains a strong finish, though close inspection will reveal minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and all electronics are fully functional, with only minor wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
